    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like a temporary \"break.\" it feels permanent. like the person who used to care about all that stuff is just... gone. i look at my work and i don't see anything. i look at the future and it's just a long, gray hallway of nothing. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's supposed to be a purpose to it all when there isn't.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
